title: Large 2-Bedroom at Grande Market Place -
posting_body: ['Grande Market Place Apartments are located in the center of the city with convenient access to shopping, transportation, schools, entertainment, 35W, and 35E.', 'It is situated in the newer development area of Burnsville which emphasizes art and cultural opportunities.', "The community offers 113 apartments with large studio, 1, & 2 bedroom apartment homes for today's diverse lifestyles.", 'Grande Market Place has exceptional community and apartment amenities that make it a great home in the "heart of the city".', '2 bedroom | 2 bath | 1,471 sq ft. | Starting at $1,504', 'Monthly Income 2X rent is required for this unit', 'For more information call :', 'show contact info', 'Apartment Amenities:', '*Walk-In Closets', 'Washer/Dryer in Unit', 'Breakfast Bar', 'Dishwasher', '*Patio/Balcony', 'Updated Carpet and Vinyl Flooring', 'Individual Climate Control', 'High Speed Internet Available', '10 Channel Satellite TV', 'Water, Sewer, Trash Included', '*In Select Units', 'Community Amenities:', '24-hour Fitness Center', 'Community Room', 'Courtyard', 'Underground Parking Available $50/month | Free Street Parking | City Ramp Availability', 'Cats Welcome (with $300 non-refundable fee | Restrictions Apply)', 'Central Air Conditioning', '24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Controlled Access Entry', 'Great Nearby Parks & Shopping', 'Close Proximity with the Burnsville Transit Center', '*Rents subject to change daily, please contact us for the most updated pricing', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
